The paper deals with the topic of smartphone user authentication, which is related to computer security (cs.CR) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The use of sensors and machine learning techniques also suggests the categories of cybernetics (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
